title: Live in Luxury in New Georgetown Property
posting_body: This new property has everything you need to feel like you're in the lap of luxury!
Within your unit you'll have granite countertops, walk-in closets, faux wood flooring, and a washer and dryer included.
Property amenities include Swimming pool with a tanning deck, kitchen and bar, and outdoor TVs, and outdoor entertainment area with game spaces.
The 24/7 fitness center is equipped with high quality machines and conditioning equipment.
Entertain in a social clubroom with a kitchen, tvs and plush seating, and wi-fi in the common areas.
You’ll also have access to a community garden, and for your pets you'll have a pet spa, pet wash space, and a large fenced in pet park.
For those who work remotely, the property includes a Work Well space with reservable private offices and a large conference room.
Pricing and Availability subject to change.
